<p>Trystan tells us <a href="https://cartography.pika.page/posts/never-look-at-your-files-again-wikilinks-tags-and-search-in-ia-writer" target="_blank">we never need to organise our files again</a>. He advocates for wikilinks, tags, and search in iA Writer.</p>
<p>My thoughts while reading this article:</p>
<ul>
